'''埃瑞克·拉汀'''（{{lang-en|Eric Ladin}}，{{bd|1978年|2月16日}}）是一位[[美國|美國]]男演員。拉汀出生在休斯敦，曾經在USC戲劇藝術學校就讀，出演過《[[酒私風雲|酒私風雲]]》等電視劇<ref>{{cite web|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|title=Eric Ladin To Recur On HBO’s ‘Boardwalk Empire’, Luke Grimes Joins ‘True Blood’|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/03/ric-ladin-to-recur-on-hbos-boardwalk-empire-luke-grimes-joins-true-blood/|publisher=Deadline|accessdate=3 April 2014|archive-date=2014-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140520133019/http://www.deadline.com/2013/03/ric-ladin-to-recur-on-hbos-boardwalk-empire-luke-grimes-joins-true-blood/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.thewrap.com/boardwalk-empire-killing-vet-eric-ladin-play-j-edgar-hoover-83021/ |title = ‘Boardwalk Empire’ Taps ‘Killing’ Vet Eric Ladin to Play J. Edgar Hoover |author = Tim Kenneally |date = 2013-03-28 |publisher = The Wrap |language = en |accessdate = 2018-08-27 |archive-date = 2020-08-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200802143516/https://www.thewrap.com/boardwalk-empire-killing-vet-eric-ladin-play-j-edgar-hoover-83021/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。拉汀是一位猶太人<ref>{{cite web|last1=Ladin|first1=Eric|title=I Met An Amazing Man Today...|url=http://www.ericladin.com/blog/|website=ericladin.com|accessdate=18 August 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141018200351/http://www.ericladin.com/blog/|archivedate=2014年10月18日}}</ref>。

